  <fr:mainmatter>
    <html:p>I wish that <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-014S.xml" title="Things.app" addr="jms-014S" type="local">Things.app</fr:link> made it possible for me to mark that a task is in progress. There is something about the ability to do this that fits well with my own need to lower the mental and spiritual weight of my pile of tasks.</html:p>
  </fr:mainmatter>
